    {
      "beat_id": "B01",
      "estimated_duration_s": 9,
      "narration_text": "This is Liam, in for Bear. Scatter an X-ray from an electron and the outgoing X-ray can return with a longer wavelength. The shift depends only on its scattering angle.",
