            "command": "Why does a scattered X-ray return with a longer wavelength?",
            "topic": "QUANTUM MECHANICS — COMPTON SCATTERING",
            "segment": "A Photon Gives Momentum to an Electron",
            "greeting": "Hallo, Liam",
            "runningText": "balancing energy and momentum…",
            "output": [
              "The electron recoils.",
              "The photon loses energy and gains wavelength."
            ],
            "folderLabel": "@NikBearBrown",
